These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, van
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | fantasy |
| Transport     | van | car  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, lacrosse
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | pepper      | lettuce         |
| Sport   | volleyball | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: plum, peach
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk   |
| Food       | peach  | plum |

 #################################

 
